Subject:For me to walk
I do not know what to start with that’s why I will start with the description of my character. I find myself quite a knowledgeable and clever girl, also I am  very kind and romantic. 

I like sea and sun. I adore just laying under the sun and receive sunbathes.. It seems to be banal to describe imaginary image of a loved one. I am looking for normal, realistic man. For me it is very important to meet my special one. Though, I can say for sure that appearance is far from being very important. 
The inner beauty is much more important than beauty of the body. I want my man to be serious, educated and very attentive. 
